{"tid":2019610,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中原城市領先指數反彈0.54%　分析料未來數周續升","createTime":"2020-05-16T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:09:27.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eedf6942248cf6e44dd7ea8cbb501ca044499370","tid":2019610,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數(CCL)報175.94，按星期回升0.54%。<br />\n<br />\n中小型單位按星期升0.58%，大型單位亦升0.3%。分區樓價個別發展，新界西升1.9%，新界東則跌1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n中原表示，CCL連續9個星期低位爭持，累積上升動力。本周樓價止跌回升，並創11個星期新高，二手成交持續暢旺，樓市新一輪升浪開始，預料未來數星期樓價指數轉勢上升。"},{"pid":"742b42438af52570df10b6f7e0864eac15e1f7f2","tid":2019610,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"真係睇唔通，睇樓同成交真係多咗"},{"pid":"4051a82ac1ea71c99c443639353d54ef806dcb36","tid":2019610,"uid":60338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"742b42438af52570df10b6f7e0864eac15e1f7f2","tid":2019610,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"真係睇唔通，睇樓同成交真係多咗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲唔反美。就係美國無限QE,過兩年上載盤1000萬啦。屌你老母侵侵"},{"pid":"6131f02c20f2cc6db71196ae5b8e2d7fbdfbd88f","tid":2019610,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4051a82ac1ea71c99c443639353d54ef806dcb36","tid":2019610,"uid":60338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"742b42438af52570df10b6f7e0864eac15e1f7f2","tid":2019610,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"真係睇唔通，睇樓同成交真係多咗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲唔反美。就係美國無限QE,過兩年上載盤1000萬啦。屌你老母侵侵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"上車盤"},{"pid":"7068c431cf674589f49ecf3336741586c6e0867c","tid":2019610,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4051a82ac1ea71c99c443639353d54ef806dcb36","tid":2019610,"uid":60338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"742b42438af52570